name: 90 App Icons for iOS or whatever -_-
description:
Made this set under hype based on iOS 14 customization... Now want to share them with Community and hope you will find this file helpful!


Laconic was real commercial product, so i also included some promo mockups for icons: landing, iPhone home screen, logo, favicon, instructions, etsy & gumroad hero images...


All icons done in Figma mostly from scratch and then flattened.
